"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Copyright is absurd, and its essence is hegemony. \\n\\nUsers can have ownership of NFT works, but no copyrights. Copycat images do not matter. The reason why someone buys NFT is a belief in scarcity. \\n\\nThen all images of my works can be licensed for free in the future. People can use the image for free, but they need to pay if they use them for commercial purposes. \\n\\nWe can make a smart contract for this. If the original NFT works are being copied, such as printing, and derivatives, then a new NFT can be generated based on this NFT. The original NFT is the parent NFT, and the newly generated NFT is the child NFT. Then we set a royalty. Every time a child-NFT is sold, the creator can get a certain share. Consumers can check the child NFT to see whether they have bought authorized products. In this way, the NFT can be bound to the physical object, an object with the NFT is the authorized object.\",\"timestamp\":1641146110,\"title\":\"Capsule（22.6.2021）Exploration of Copyright Issues: Parent and Child NFT Contract\"},\"digest\":\"e7ZZoegxe55xtH4CRRv-k5ktpSaiVYEjXY8qGj8i_dE\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xE828f8bE1a3CB994133936fB4D9A708a7D192462\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"cWndKezD0ZiMgnYOqspWtyALlI_KYDziYOZaOerHeCY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Kf7VHolS02uUcQvJnvpP7ci_9wxCwvj1KsxIdy1wyS4\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"CrdBx9RwUGtazEq_BWq4oTPacY8Ffe2SrB8rrIzv40yG1vUni0f0tYOgmW-EFWwPBZ4KxDDvvyV3F1BiTIyQkg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x24845bd906a3dcd3a6a2c8def0e1867a94aa37e04d35018a13b94099ae5be24d4b1abdd27984d765963fd65aa852fe7e1dc6d3934335a6e14328e5bca1565db21b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"cWndKezD0ZiMgnYOqspWtyALlI_KYDziYOZaOerHeCY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Kf7VHolS02uUcQvJnvpP7ci_